{"tid":1694563,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我準備好攬炒了 你願意罷工未","createTime":"2019-11-05T08:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T08:34:34.000Z","uid":113368,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2f871c3e586b74d26a6bd877566a5e93a7a54a01","tid":1694563,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"願佢來生不用再誕生在這地獄鬼國 <br />\n示威完不用再俾黑社會打 <br />\n不用再躲避催淚彈"},{"pid":"1c09512049ffd3996058290d12573623c71d4dcf","tid":1694563,"uid":113368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我要攬炒呀</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"26cd94172fa4490c91c55ae8e2faba924f25fe6f","tid":1694563,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:19:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攬炒！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒！！再攬炒！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">反正香港人打狗最多都係打兩棍<br />\n無可能力敵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只有經濟攬炒，香港人先會贏！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">共狗開始急了，要班popo發癲，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊就係咁出新聞話暴力就黎完。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎緊又SOGO感謝祭，又聖誕新年，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係攬炒既最好機會！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[認清重心]經濟攬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691857</a><